      <scopecontent id="aspace_6d0a1357aa6959c5fdd8171a951e3212">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of forty-eight black and white postcards from the Belgian Propoganda Ministry following the invasion of German East Africa in 1917. Although German forces in German East Africa were never defeated, the postcards show 'Occupied' German East Africa.</p>  
